data.description: Welcome to your coastal dream retreat in Hertford, North Carolina! In the gated community of Albemarle Plantation. This remarkable 4-bedroom, 5-bathroom home, crafted in 2009, offers an expansive 6,327 square feet of luxury living. The convenience of one-level living is yours with the primary bedroom thoughtfully situated on the first floor, providing ease and comfort. Nestled in a serene neighborhood with its own golf course, you'll enjoy both the tranquility of this peaceful community and the excitement of the game. For water enthusiasts, the nearby marina offers an incredible 166 boat slips, making it a boater's paradise. With many more amenities to explore and a spacious, well-appointed, custom  interior, this residence truly embodies the best of coastal living in the heart of Hertford, NC.  THIS LOVELY HOME IS BEING SOLD AS IS WITH A $15K BUYER USE AS YOU CHOOSE
